### Get all accounts
GET http://localhost:8080/client-api/accounts
Accept: application/json

###

### Get account by ID (replace {id} with actual ID, e.g., 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/client-api/accounts/1
Accept: application/json

###

    ### Create a new account
POST http://localhost:8080/client-api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "johndoe123",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "USER",
  "active": true,
  "creationDate": "2024-02-03T10:00:00",
  "client": {
    "id": 1
  }
